      "id": "PopularPost154582",
      "post_content": "When this was printed there was no exlie zone. [Swords to Plowshares](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Swords to Plowshares) or [Disintegrate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disintegrate) removed the creature from the game, so this ring could have gotten it back. This is what wishes can do btw.  \n  \nSo it should be re-oracled to allow cards in exile.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost154582\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">When this was printed there was no exlie zone. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Swords to Plowshares\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Swords to Plowshares\">Swords to Plowshares</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Disintegrate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Disintegrate\">Disintegrate</a> removed the creature from the game, so this ring could have gotten it back. This is what wishes can do btw.<br/><br/>So it should be re-oracled to allow cards in exile.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '154582'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (4/27/2011 12:49:00 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.