      "id": "PopularPost109193",
      "post_content": "@nerman8r: Actually, the oracle wording is right on. Cards that have been removed from the game (\"Exiled\", in the common parlance) are actually still in the game, albeit in the \"removed from game zone\" (Now the \"exiled\" zone).",
